+# Pruned
+
+- Sort-key registry / strategy map (text -> keyfunc, id -> ..., created -> ...):
+  rejected. Only one variant (`text`) is required NOW. An abstraction for
+  future keys needs >=2 real variants; until then it is speculative.
+- Sorting inside store.load(): rejected. Ordering is a presentation concern;
+  the store is the single source of truth in insertion order. Keeps the seam small.
